      <section id="id12339229">
        <title>Activity 1: SUPPLY CURVE</title>
        <para id="id8670750">Make use of the data supplied in the table above and draw the supply curve. Insert it on a separate page.</para>
        <para id="id14370580">From this the LAW OF SUPPLY can be deduced, which states that <emphasis effect="italics">“the number / quantity of goods that are offered will rise in proportion to rises, in the price and vice versa, namely that the number / quantity supplied will fall when the price shows a decline”.</emphasis></para>
      </section>
