        <para id="id14039477">The price that a consumer is willing to pay for a product depends mainly on (1) how urgent his need is and (2) the amount of money that the consumer has available. Here we have to do with the DEMAND for a product or products that is / are valid at a specific price, in specific numbers / quantity and at a specific time. Once again it is possible that the indicated prices and numbers / amounts may differ from day to day.</para>
