      <section id="id12342764">
        <title>Activity 3: DEMAND CURVE</title>
        <para id="id3270851">Make use of the data supplied in the table above and draw the demand curve. Insert it on a separate page.</para>
        <para id="id8686052">From this the LAW OF DEMAND can be deduced, which states that <emphasis effect="italics">“the number / quantity demanded will rise in proportion to the decline in price, and vice versa, namely that the number / quantity demanded will fall when the price shows an inclination to rise”.</emphasis></para>
        <para id="id7867673">Draw up a list of the factors that will influence the number / quantity demanded.</para>
        <table id="id12568532" summary="">
          <tgroup cols="2">
